column2: A great university located along the California coast!
They say it's the happiest place on earth, and I haven't seen anything to prove otherwise.
Literally the worst theater I've ever been to. It's dirty and old, but it has charm.
All the degens of Gilroy hang out there. I'm always afraid that I might get stabbed. 5 stars.
In October, they put on the Halloween Haunt. It's not scary, but I hate clowns and they can honestly catch these hands when they jump out to scare me.
A park near my house - kind of lame, but has some gnarly Pokemon for people who played Pokemon Go like 3 years ago.
